https://blog.csdn.net/warnerwu/article/details/73381611

1.创建php用户和组:
[root@localhost ~]# groupadd -r php
[root@localhost ~]# useradd -r -g php -s /sbin/nologin -d /usr/local/php -M php

2.安装一些php的依赖
[root@stackoverflowchina1 ~]# yum -y install ifconfig libxml2 libxml2-devel openssl openssl-devel bzip2 bzip2-devel \
libcurl libcurl-devel libjpeg libjpeg-devel libpng libpng-devel freetype freetype-devel libzip \
gmp gmp-devel libmcrypt libmcrypt-devel readline readline-devel libxslt libxslt-devel tcl-devel \
httpd glibc krb5-libs pcre zlib gperftools-libs net-tools pcre-devel gcc-c++ zlib-devel ruby patch \
bash-completion lsof unzip zip gcc libicu-devel libc-client-devel openldap  openldap-devel curl-devel libwebp libwebp-devel \
bzip2 bzip2-devel

下面这个有需要再安装
yum -y groupinstall "Development Tools"

在后面所有操作都完成之后记得执行一次:
yum -y update

3.安装php7
[root@stackoverflowchina1 ~]# wget http://cn2.php.net/distributions/php-7.2.5.tar.gz
下载太慢了 可以先在本地下载好然后通过scp上传
$ scp ~/Documents/php-7.2.5.tar.gz root@192.168.242.128:/root

编译安装:
./configure \
--prefix=/usr/local/php \
--with-config-file-path=/etc \
--with-config-file-scan-dir=/etc/php.d \
--enable-fpm \
--with-fpm-user=nginx \
--with-fpm-group=nginx \
--enable-inline-optimization \
--disable-debug \
--disable-rpath \
--enable-shared \
--enable-soap \
--with-libxml-dir \
--with-xmlrpc \
--with-openssl \
--with-mhash \
--with-pcre-regex \
--with-sqlite3 \
--with-zlib \
--enable-bcmath \
--with-iconv \
--with-bz2 \
--enable-calendar \
--with-curl \
--with-cdb \
--enable-dom \
--enable-exif \
--enable-fileinfo \
--enable-filter \
--with-pcre-dir \
--enable-ftp \
--with-gd \
--with-openssl-dir \
--with-jpeg-dir \
--with-png-dir \
--with-zlib-dir \
--with-freetype-dir \
--enable-gd-jis-conv \
--with-gettext \
--with-gmp \
--with-mhash \
--enable-json \
--enable-mbstring \
--enable-mbregex \
--enable-mbregex-backtrack \
--with-libmbfl \
--with-onig \
--enable-pdo \
--with-mysqli=mysqlnd \
--with-pdo-mysql=mysqlnd \
--with-pdo-sqlite \
--with-readline \
--enable-session \
--enable-shmop \
--enable-simplexml \
--enable-sockets \
--enable-sysvmsg \
--enable-sysvsem \
--enable-sysvshm \
--enable-wddx \
--with-libxml-dir \
--with-xsl \
--enable-zip \
--enable-mysqlnd \
--with-pear \
--enable-opcache \
--with-pcre-jit \
--enable-intl \
--with-iconv-dir \
--with-webp-dir \
--enable-fast-install

编译:
make 

编译后测试:
make test

测试没有问题就安装,一般需要超级用户权限:
[sudo] make install
Installing shared extensions:     /usr/local/php/lib/php/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20170718/
Installing PHP CLI binary:        /usr/local/php/bin/
Installing PHP CLI man page:      /usr/local/php/php/man/man1/
